reviews.review_text:
Wow! Great Half-Step, Brown-Eyed, Let It Grow and PITB... only Dew of '78, it's not a '77 Dew but i's still nice.

'78 wants listening to with your ears and not with your pre-conceived notions before being dismissed, some great Betty Board upgrades coming through lately... enjoy!
Only Morning Dew in 78 And most of 79 too!
